Class Views.Cells

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.brokenswing.comixaire.view.Views.Cells
  • Enclosing class:
    Views

    public static final class Views.Cells
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used as a namespace. It encapsulates views that are meant to be used as cells for ListViews.
